locality: Soalala subprefecture, commune de Andranomavo, Reserve Natural Tsingy de Namoroka, NE side, ca. 1,5 km of camp.Vegetation: deciduous forest with evergreen elements in Tsingy forest island. Habitat: undisturbed forest surounded by tsingy, humus-rich soil, climbe or small tree. Geology: loany sand soil over limestone.
